data.description: Whether you seek a tranquil HOMESTEAD or an INVESTMENT lot to be subdivided, this centrally located property is a rare find. With .61 acres & centrally located between Downtown and Clarkston Heights, you can bring your ANIMALS to graze the fenced in pasture. The house has a unique 3bed + 2bath layout, real HARDWOOD floors, wood fireplace, and tons of natural character you won't find anywhere else. Don't forget the detached 2 car garage and WORKSHOP. This property truly has endless potential to be shaped into the sanctuary you've been searching for!
